things to remeber : - i think he likes sandwiches.... - i found out he also likes unicorns... ♥ ♥ ♥

Today i saw jake sitting still on a hill, for SO LONG at first i thought it was funny and weird, but then got a little worried weeelll long story short, he is GREAT at meditaiting Hes not especially centered or "focused", but, i guess he just got that in him... he got that DOG in him.. hehe

Oh maaann :( :( I gave him some of my stuff, just to hold them for a sec bc... it was heavy and i was tired!! but then i forgot about it!! ...And then I think he thinks, i just -gave- it to him bc i didn't want those things or something :(
Today i found out he knows how to cook really well !! He makes the BEST sandwiches EVER ...im not that crazy about it though :P Im really proud of my old bro :)

If someday he's gone, i dont know what i would do without him
I think i would go find him.
Yeah, i would i'll go find him, wherever he is.
